
Major functionality:
    *General attack against other generals
    *General attack against territories
    Territory defence separate from counter-attacks by inhabiting generals
    Stamina used for actions
    Choice of general given for each action within a specific territory
    Each turn-segment cycles through all loyal generals/governors in owned territories
    Land generates resources on a set schedule
    Land can be improved for greater resource gain
    Fortifications can be made and improved for defence against attacking generals
    Territory defence separate from counter-attacks by inhabiting generals
